<li>Claire Harman, <i>Robert Louis Stevenson: A Biography</i>, HarperCollins, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0007113218" class="internal">ISBN 0-00-711321-8</a> [reviewed by Matthew Sturgis in the <i><a href="/wiki/Times_Literary_Supplement" title="Times Literary Supplement" class="mw-redirect">Times Literary Supplement</a></i>, 11 March 2005, page 8]</li>
