<li>Roland Paxton, "Stevenson, Thomas (1818-1887)", <i><a href="/wiki/Oxford_Dictionary_of_National_Biography#Oxford_Dictionary_of_National_Biography" title="Oxford Dictionary of National Biography" class="mw-redirect">Oxford Dictionary of National Biography</a></i>, Oxford: OUP, 2004. Retrieved on 11 October 2008</li>
