<li><a href="http://www.riapress.com/riapress/author.lasso?goto=35&amp;-session=StoreSession:51ECA750050e324ACDGMYQB32E41" class="external text" title="http://www.riapress.com/riapress/author.lasso?goto=35&amp;-session=StoreSession:51ECA750050e324ACDGMYQB32E41" rel="nofollow">Works by Robert Louis Stevenson</a> in PDF at <a href="/w/index.php?title=Ria_Press&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Ria Press (page does not exist)">Ria Press</a>.</li>
<li>Stevenson's writings in <a href="/wiki/Scots_language" title="Scots language">Scots</a> at <a href="http://www.scotstext.org/makars/robert_louis_stevenson/" class="external text" title="http://www.scotstext.org/makars/robert_louis_stevenson/" rel="nofollow">ScotsteXt</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Biographies_and_commentaries" id="Biographies_and_commentaries"></a></p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline">Biographies and commentaries</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>There are over <a href="http://dinamico.unibg.it/rls/biogs.htm" class="external text" title="http://dinamico.unibg.it/rls/biogs.htm" rel="nofollow">200 published biographies of RLS</a></li>
<li><i><a href="http://www.gutenberg.net/etext/590" class="external text" title="http://www.gutenberg.net/etext/590" rel="nofollow">Robert Louis Stevenson: a record, an estimate, and a memorial</a></i>, by <a href="/w/index.php?title=Alexander_H._Japp&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Alexander H. Japp (page does not exist)">Alexander H. Japp</a></li>
<li><i><a href="http://www.gutenberg.net/etext/333" class="external text" title="http://www.gutenberg.net/etext/333" rel="nofollow">Robert Louis Stevenson</a></i>, a biography by Sir <a href="/wiki/Walter_Raleigh_(professor)" title="Walter Raleigh (professor)">Walter Alexander Raleigh</a></li>
<li><a href="http://books.google.com/books?vid=OCLC00502469&amp;id=8omQokmMv7IC&amp;pg=RA1-PA287&amp;lpg=RA1-PA287&amp;dq=stevenson+inauthor:edmund+inauthor:gosse&amp;num=100#PRA1-PA275,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?vid=OCLC00502469&amp;id=8omQokmMv7IC&amp;pg=RA1-PA287&amp;lpg=RA1-PA287&amp;dq=stevenson+inauthor:edmund+inauthor:gosse&amp;num=100#PRA1-PA275,M1" rel="nofollow">Robert Louis Stevenson: a memoir</a> (1895), by <a href="/wiki/Edmund_Gosse" title="Edmund Gosse">Edmund Gosse</a> who knew Stevenson personally.</li>
<li><a href="http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&amp;id=ahwOAAAAIAAJ&amp;dq=graham+balfour+life+of+robert+louis+stevenson&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=web&amp;ots=bWzWrnfJ6J&amp;sig=3ulX-IRZwmlKtqA9FyLn7fHtSdQ" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&amp;id=ahwOAAAAIAAJ&amp;dq=graham+balfour+life+of+robert+louis+stevenson&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=web&amp;ots=bWzWrnfJ6J&amp;sig=3ulX-IRZwmlKtqA9FyLn7fHtSdQ" rel="nofollow">The Life of Robert Louis Stevenson</a> (1913) by Graham Balfour, Stevenson's cousin.</li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Robert_Louis_Stevenson:_a_short_biography" class="external text" title="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Robert_Louis_Stevenson:_a_short_biography" rel="nofollow">Robert Louis Stevenson: biography</a> (1911), by <a href="/wiki/Edmund_Gosse" title="Edmund Gosse">Edmund Gosse</a>, from the <i><a href="/wiki/Encyclop%C3%A6dia_Britannica_Eleventh_Edition" title="Encyclopædia Britannica Eleventh Edition">Encyclopædia Britannica Eleventh Edition</a></i></li>
<li><a href="http://people.brandeis.edu/~teuber/stevensonbio.html" class="external text" title="http://people.brandeis.edu/~teuber/stevensonbio.html" rel="nofollow">Robert Louis Stevenson</a>, biography from the <i>Dictionary of Literary Biography</i>, 1987.</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Misc" id="Misc"></a></p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline">Misc</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://dinamico.unibg.it/rls/rls.htm" class="external text" title="http://dinamico.unibg.it/rls/rls.htm" rel="nofollow">Robert Louis Stevenson Website</a>. Extensive information including the most complete collection of derivative works. Maintained by editor of the <a href="http://www.english.stir.ac.uk/centres/stevensonstudies.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.english.stir.ac.uk/centres/stevensonstudies.htm" rel="nofollow"><i>Journal of Stevenson Studies</i></a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.bellrock.org.uk/stevensons/" class="external text" title="http://www.bellrock.org.uk/stevensons/" rel="nofollow">The bell rock lighthouse and the Stevensons: the history of an old sea tower and a family of engineers</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.gr70-stevenson.com/en/stevenson-trail.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.gr70-stevenson.com/en/stevenson-trail.htm" rel="nofollow">Robert Louis Stevenson trail GR70</a></li>
